# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is generally recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
#   This is especially recommended for binary packages to ensure reproducible builds.
#   However, if you need to support multiple versions of python, you will need to do this
#   in pyproject.toml and not include poetry.lock
#poetry.lock

